After running this command:
{code}
setsebool -P eucalyptus_storage_controller 1
{code}
The SC became enabled.  I guess that's the issue then.  This isn't set automatically after installation.  There is documentation on this as well:  https://docs.eucalyptus.com/eucalyptus/latest/#install-guide/configure_selinux.html
